{"tid":1242251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行動升級要堅持勇武 唔係等比狗打或者不合作","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T03:06:40.000Z","uid":202952,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9449d11128a7728812efcaa690ee1ff91da539e6","tid":1242251,"uid":202952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:44:07.000Z","msg":"依家多人支持 更加應該發夢嗰陣提升武力 喺政府唔回應訴求之下 出師有名咁衝撃 真係入到去政總或者立會參觀 <br />\n<br />\n令本屆立法會通過唔到其他法案 就已經係癱痪政府 比不仺作運動更有bargaining power 又唔會阻到其他人返工 民意反而唔會流失"},{"pid":"9e937476515854880c38e8c314fd4cdc1461b84b","tid":1242251,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:45:25.000Z","msg":"而家已經集體批鬥勇武<br />\n泛民又想選舉<br />\n仲有咩可以玩"},{"pid":"68247ef072b7a6311177bf10e40f25ad0123db97","tid":1242251,"uid":169141,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:46:30.000Z","msg":"出面個個po都講雞蛋　乜真係可行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804f14749b863813d70ecca1f5989064da43b338","tid":1242251,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5045bc02e99c31acda94b882499a9dcc64709c82","tid":1242251,"uid":202952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:47:58.000Z","msg":"希望出面唔好再話玩雞蛋 要入到立會唔比佢開會先有用"},{"pid":"cf7f5225705c19cbaeb7da0157b07392d9df54b1","tid":1242251,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:48:59.000Z","msg":"勇武先代表真，升級"},{"pid":"7484efedefa09d881f522759b8687494ce1c3699","tid":1242251,"uid":202952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:53:03.000Z","msg":"好多人真係唔睇國際新聞<br />\n淨係用心靈感應去感應啲記者點諗<br />\n其實就算香港記者，好多都support勇武<br />\n你諗下佢地永遠企喺比前線更前既地方，眼中根本就無和理非既存在<br />\n根本勇武就唔會流失國際support"},{"pid":"02de6a467a5fe1605963f28dfe39d16cb35bd1a3","tid":1242251,"uid":202952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:22:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eb96fbccad6ecb3014369f5ac0541b59a325ded4","tid":1242251,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:26:45.000Z","msg":"和理非入嚟睇下應該點做<br />\n<br />\n唔想和理非同勇武再互屌就全部同我入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1241634\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1241634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"db6bc937984c9ddc3056d9304d9582ae9726648d","tid":1242251,"uid":202952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:37:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9668b40bba0baf8605957f775212aa1b72e3cd46","tid":1242251,"uid":202952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:51:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a331b87be4e07abe8e37cf2263b002cc85d5fe10","tid":1242251,"uid":202952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:25:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f69c9760b0237cb75a5c66910f03528a0ba52d6a","tid":1242251,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:32:14.000Z","msg":"樓主你勸掂出面班人先"},{"pid":"0d2e805cedba24de00a34e7dbc76ee2e200b01bf","tid":1242251,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:33:51.000Z","msg":"[各位又要辛苦了] 請預備好資料同長輩圖, 今年24/11區選同出年立法會選舉要全港藍絲廢老齊齊反共<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242605</a>"},{"pid":"634fd706b9747fb37823fe21bc2635d61bfb4c42","tid":1242251,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:00:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3eeb6d7b3fc8328c9602a6b0553dcebbd972ee6","tid":1242251,"uid":202952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:06:40.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}